00:01:40,240 --> 00:01:42,960
The Prince of Tennis
~ Match! Tennis Juniors! ~

20
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:48,920
It's men's business,
let the skills speak for you.

21
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:51,560
