22
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:53,920
This place is just fine, let's play here.

23
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:55,320
This is a court for doubles.

24
00:01:58,880 --> 00:01:59,800
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

25
00:02:00,880 --> 00:02:02,080
[both gasp]

26
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:04,600
[whooshes]

27
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:07,080
-[grunts]
-Lu Xia.

28
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:11,039
Leave. Next.

29
00:02:12,040 --> 00:02:13,520
You just don't cooperate.

30
00:02:13,759 --> 00:02:16,320
[man 1] Whoa! You two surely are
the top doubles couple in Yu Hang.

31
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,440
Yu Hang High School?

32
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,920
They are our opponents
in the next competition.

33
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:23,160
-[man 2] Do you have a way on how to win?
-[man 3] They are not a match for you.

34
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,240
[sighs]

35
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:31,040
-How do you practice tennis?
-We would like to learn from you

36
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:33,040
-and observe your skills.
-[man 4] Exactly.

37
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:35,640
Qiao, I have come up with an idea.

38
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,120
Qiao Chen.

39
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:46,160
[romantic music]

40
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,680
[soft chuckle]

41
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:56,080
Hi, Qiao Chen.

42
00:02:58,880 --> 00:03:01,400
Xing Zi, when did you arrive?

43
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,720
I came a little earlier than you two.

44
00:03:07,200 --> 00:03:08,400
So, you saw everything?

45
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:09,960
Yes.

46
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:13,240
Who is she?

47
00:03:14,040 --> 00:03:16,360
[sighs, clicks tongue]

48
00:03:16,440 --> 00:03:17,680
My classmate from junior high.

49
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:20,000
If I knew she was there,
I would have tried my best.

50
00:03:20,480 --> 00:03:22,720
[sighs]
Qiao Chen, I thought it through.

51
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,080
I gave up the third.

52
00:03:25,760 --> 00:03:26,920
I think so.

53
00:03:28,320 --> 00:03:30,720
[both] Men should play doubles.

54
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:37,600
[light music]

55
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:47,000
Well, what do you want to drink?

56
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:52,400
-[Xing Zi] This one is fine.
-Okay.

57
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:55,080
[whirring]

58
00:03:55,920 --> 00:03:57,480
[beeps, whirs]

59
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:03,960
[soft chuckle]

60
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:05,160
Stop.

61
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:07,680
You drink this.

62
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:09,960
[chuckles]

63
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:13,120
Hmm. Twisting the cap is a basic skill.

64
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:15,480
Why are you still naive
just like in junior high?

65
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:19,079
You saw me earlier.

66
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:21,000
Why didn't you come and say hello?

67
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:23,079
I wanted to observe first.

68
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,200
Observe?

69
00:04:24,279 --> 00:04:27,200
It's rare to watch an unofficial match
between Yu Qing and Yu Hang.

70
00:04:27,280 --> 00:04:29,280
I wanted to see
which school has a stronger team.

71
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:33,320
You didn't have to watch.
We are certainly the stronger one.

72
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:35,880
-That's not what I saw.
-Hmm!

73
00:04:37,640 --> 00:04:39,840
That's because it was Lu Xia's first time
to play doubles.

74
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:41,840
We didn't have a chance
to show our real strength.

75
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:43,160
[inhales sharply]

76
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:45,520
That freshman is the ace
of your school team?

77
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:47,640
Sure, he is the...

78
00:04:50,400 --> 00:04:51,240
Eh?

79
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:52,320
Where is he?

80
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:54,400
He left us earlier.

81
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:56,360
You didn't realize it until now?

82
00:04:57,840 --> 00:04:58,840
Huh?

83
00:05:00,080 --> 00:05:01,600
[crickets creaking]

84
00:05:21,440 --> 00:05:23,320
A GUIDE ON TENNIS DOUBLES

85
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:26,480
Are you staying up late
to learn how to play doubles?

86
00:05:26,840 --> 00:05:27,760
Yes.

87
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:34,320
The most important thing
for tennis doubles is coordination.

88
00:05:34,400 --> 00:05:35,840
Then come the techniques. Understand?

89
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:37,880
[chuckles]

90
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:42,560
So you should read this instead.

91
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:47,160
A BASIC COURSE ON TENNIS DOUBLES
FOR BEGINNERS

92
00:05:54,440 --> 00:05:56,160
[men grunting]

93
00:06:01,320 --> 00:06:02,680
[camera shutter clicking]

94
00:06:03,280 --> 00:06:04,240
[man grunts]

95
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:11,920
[gasping]

96
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:15,760
-Lu Xia, can I interview you?
-No.

97
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:17,520
Oh.

98
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:25,560
-[thwacks]
-[men grunting]

99
00:06:29,400 --> 00:06:30,720
-Hey.
-[gasps]

100
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:33,520
This is not a place for interviewing.

101
00:06:34,440 --> 00:06:36,600
Plus, high-heeled shoes
are not allowed in the court.

102
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:37,800
Please leave at once.

103
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:39,360
Okay.

104
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,560
[camera shutter clicking]

105
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:05,120
Is there anybody here?

106
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,800
I am coming in.

107
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:16,320
[sighs]
I will just change clothes here.

108
00:07:20,440 --> 00:07:21,480
[exhales sharply]

109
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:31,880
Luckily, I have spare clothes in my car.

110
00:07:35,520 --> 00:07:37,520
[light music]

111
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:42,920
[humming]

112
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:51,600
-[camera shutter clicks]
-[door opens]

113
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:54,680
[comical music]

114
00:07:55,520 --> 00:07:57,320
-[gasping]
-[camera shutter clicking]

115
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:01,840
[Xiuwen screams]

116
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:06,080
[indistinct chatter]

117
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:11,160
[gasping]

118
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:17,480
Little boy, I will show you
what I am capable of.

119
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:20,320
[Ying] Oh. Hi, Miss Reporter.

120
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:22,480
Why are you still here?

121
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:26,520
Can you still recognize me
even if I dress up like this?

122
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:29,160
[soft chuckle]
Because of your employee ID.

123
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:31,640
[chuckles]

124
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:33,520
Well...
[clears throat]

125
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:35,720
I have something important to do.

126
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:37,039
Keep this a secret.

127
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:39,520
-Don't follow me. Bye.
-Oh.

128
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:42,320
-Bye.
-Bye.

129
00:08:44,280 --> 00:08:46,280
[light music]

130
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,800
[birds chirping]

131
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,280
[exhales sharply]

132
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:05,440
-[gasps]
-Xiao Sha.

133
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:08,480
Haven't I told you not to follow me?
Why are you doing it again?

134
00:09:09,160 --> 00:09:11,080
This is my way home.

135
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,760
Oh.
[gasps]

136
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:15,720
Okay, you should go home now.

137
00:09:16,040 --> 00:09:18,560
I'm busy. I will make a big impact
on sports education in China.

138
00:09:18,640 --> 00:09:19,560
[clicks tongue]

139
00:09:19,640 --> 00:09:20,640
Oh.

140
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:22,000
[Sha] Where is he?

141
00:09:24,520 --> 00:09:25,520
I lost him again.

142
00:09:26,640 --> 00:09:27,480
[Sha sighs]

143
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:29,880
Ying.

144
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:32,000
Do you know where Lu Xia lives?

145
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:35,200
I do. Number 118 on Fu Guang Road.

146
00:09:35,520 --> 00:09:36,880
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

147
00:09:37,360 --> 00:09:38,520
You didn't ask me.

148
00:09:39,280 --> 00:09:40,920
Ahh.

149
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:42,880
Okay.

150
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:46,080
Since you helped me
with a big problem today,

151
00:09:46,800 --> 00:09:48,920
I will send you a handsome photo
of Lu Xia.

152
00:09:49,280 --> 00:09:50,560
-As soon as I have one.
-[gaps]

153
00:09:50,640 --> 00:09:51,720
[soft chuckle]

154
00:10:02,920 --> 00:10:03,880
[sighs]

155
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:06,840
[exhales sharply]
Here it is.

156
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:14,600
[water trickling]

157
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:26,920
♪ It's far, it's far away ♪

158
00:10:29,040 --> 00:10:33,720
♪ It's far, it's far away ♪

159
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,160
Whoa!

160
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:37,760
It really looks like
a tennis master's home.

161
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:40,880
♪ Because I have impulses
Behind my silence ♪

162
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:42,680
[clears throat]

163
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:44,880
Hello.

164
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:47,120
[Xiangqian] One room or two?

165
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:48,960
Are you Mr. Lu Xiangqian?

166
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:52,440
[chuckles]

167
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,320
That's right.

168
00:10:55,560 --> 00:10:57,640
I am Lu Xiangqian,
the owner of this homestay.

169
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:58,720
I will show you the rooms.

170
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:01,320
I am a reporter for Monthly Tennis.
You can call me Xiao Sha.

171
00:11:01,400 --> 00:11:03,680
You are my fan...
No, I am your tennis fan.

172
00:11:05,160 --> 00:11:07,000
I forgot, he's not here. I am not him.

173
00:11:07,400 --> 00:11:09,480
But you said you are Lu Xiangqian.

174
00:11:09,560 --> 00:11:15,160
♪ It's far, it's far away ♪

175
00:11:17,440 --> 00:11:18,840
Do you like...

176
00:11:19,920 --> 00:11:21,240
Hua Chenyu?

177
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,520
Why? Do you like him, too?

178
00:11:22,920 --> 00:11:23,880
[chuckles]

179
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:28,480
My close friend happens to be
an employee in his company.

180
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:33,440
I happen to have his autographed pictures
and some of his products.

181
00:11:33,520 --> 00:11:35,840
-Really?
-Of course.

182
00:11:35,920 --> 00:11:37,120
Do you have his photo album?

183
00:11:37,560 --> 00:11:38,480
Of course.

184
00:11:38,560 --> 00:11:41,200
[chuckles]
But I will only give it to Lu Xiangqian.

185
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:43,080
Since you are not him,

186
00:11:43,160 --> 00:11:45,840
-sorry and goodbye.
-I am Lu Xiangqian.

187
00:11:45,920 --> 00:11:47,080
You can ask anything you want.

188
00:11:47,680 --> 00:11:48,720
Great!

189
00:11:48,800 --> 00:11:53,320
I want to know about the real reason
why you retired.

190
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:54,760
I cannot answer that.

191
00:11:55,520 --> 00:11:56,480
[Sha gasps]

192
00:11:56,560 --> 00:11:59,360
I have a ticket to his concert.

193
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:02,800
That's funny.
Do you think I am that shallow?

194
00:12:03,280 --> 00:12:04,960
[gasps]
Uh...

195
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:06,240
Come. Sit.

196
00:12:07,680 --> 00:12:08,520
Oh.

197
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:12,400
[Sha chuckles softly]

198
00:12:13,160 --> 00:12:16,400
I really came here with good intentions.

199
00:12:16,880 --> 00:12:19,560
I know you were a legend
in the tennis world back then.

200
00:12:19,640 --> 00:12:22,880
I really want to know
how you started your tennis career.

201
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:24,440
Thank you.
[gasps]

202
00:12:24,520 --> 00:12:27,600
And why you chose to retire,

203
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:30,200
including your relationship with Lu Xia.
Thank you.

204
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:32,960
-Uh, all of these...
-You have too many questions.

205
00:12:33,040 --> 00:12:34,280
I have thought it through...

206
00:12:34,760 --> 00:12:35,800
Mr. Lu Xiangqian.

207
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:38,040
I dare you to have a competition with me.

208
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:39,360
A tennis competition?

209
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:44,080
-Can you play tennis?
-Yes.

210
00:12:44,800 --> 00:12:47,800
If I win,
you have to accept my interview...

211
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:50,600
[exhales sharply]

212
00:12:50,680 --> 00:12:52,320
...but you need to give me
a chance to win.

213
00:12:58,880 --> 00:12:59,960
Let's make a deal.

214
00:13:00,440 --> 00:13:04,520
If you can make one ball out of three
drop to the ground behind me,

215
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:07,360
-I will answer your questions.
-Is that the racket you are going to use?

216
00:13:07,760 --> 00:13:09,240
Why? Do you have a problem with that?

217
00:13:09,640 --> 00:13:12,680
-No, I am fine. Let's get started.
-Wait.

218
00:13:15,520 --> 00:13:16,560
I forgot to shake hands.

219
00:13:19,880 --> 00:13:21,880
[light music]

220
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:29,520
[exhales deeply]

221
00:13:38,400 --> 00:13:39,400
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

222
00:13:40,040 --> 00:13:41,000
[thwacks]

223
00:13:41,520 --> 00:13:42,880
Did you train in tennis?

224
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:45,200
[grunts]
Am I good?

225
00:13:45,920 --> 00:13:46,920
What do you think?

226
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:48,640
[panting]

227
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:53,360
My parents forced me to play tennis,
so this is the best I can do.

228
00:13:53,680 --> 00:13:56,200
If you weren't interested at all,
then you shouldn't have to play.

229
00:13:56,280 --> 00:13:57,320
[Sha] What about Lu Xia?

230
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:00,640
Was he interested in playing tennis?

231
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:02,000
Of course.

232
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:04,480
But he was just a child then.

233
00:14:04,920 --> 00:14:08,400
If you treat them as mere kids,
you would have underestimated them.

234
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:09,320
[soft chuckle]

235
00:14:09,400 --> 00:14:12,520
They are just senior high school students.
You are giving them too much credit.

236
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:13,680
[Xiangqian] Then...

237
00:14:14,400 --> 00:14:16,640
how mature can adults be?
You and me for example.

238
00:14:17,040 --> 00:14:18,880
[sighs]
I can't say you are a mature adult.

239
00:14:19,400 --> 00:14:20,520
[laughs]

240
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:24,480
Why did you retire at that time?

241
00:14:24,560 --> 00:14:25,400
[grunts]

242
00:14:26,520 --> 00:14:27,360
[thwacks]

243
00:14:27,440 --> 00:14:28,680
[Xiangqian] It is a secret.

244
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:31,400
[sighing]

245
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:35,360
There is no fun in playing like this.
Let me think.

246
00:14:38,800 --> 00:14:39,640
Hey.

247
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:41,480
Why don't we play this way?

248
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:46,240
[action music]

249
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:48,840
You are mocking me.

250
00:14:54,520 --> 00:14:55,440
Come on.

251
00:14:56,080 --> 00:14:58,160
Why did you bring your son back to China?

252
00:14:58,240 --> 00:14:59,880
Because the learning atmosphere is better.

253
00:15:00,160 --> 00:15:02,200
What do you think matters most
in playing tennis?

254
00:15:02,280 --> 00:15:03,520
[whooshes]

255
00:15:04,480 --> 00:15:06,800
[Xiangqian] What do you think matters most
in playing tennis?

256
00:15:06,880 --> 00:15:08,280
[Lu Xia] Winning, of course.

257
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:12,760
[tense music]

258
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:19,960
[thwacks, whooshes]

259
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:25,880
What matters most is...

260
00:15:26,440 --> 00:15:27,920
It's focus and hard work, right?

261
00:15:30,120 --> 00:15:31,880
It is happiness, of course.

262
00:15:31,960 --> 00:15:33,280
[laughs]

263
00:15:33,360 --> 00:15:34,200
[sighs]

264
00:15:34,880 --> 00:15:36,760
If only my parents knew it,
it would be great.

265
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:40,800
Forget it. Let's call it a day.
I am no match for you.

266
00:15:41,280 --> 00:15:42,840
I will find other ways to interview you.

267
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:50,520
-The food I've cooked is good, right?
-It is tasty.

268
00:15:50,600 --> 00:15:52,840
Now, you have tasted my cooking
and played tennis with me.

269
00:15:53,120 --> 00:15:55,760
I have roasted pig kidney
that you can take home.

270
00:15:55,840 --> 00:15:56,680
Thank you.

271
00:15:56,760 --> 00:15:59,800
But will you keep your promise? Huh?

272
00:15:59,880 --> 00:16:01,720
Don't forget his autographed photo.

273
00:16:01,800 --> 00:16:03,200
Oh, and also the photo album.

274
00:16:03,840 --> 00:16:05,080
[Sha] I'll take care of it.

275
00:16:05,640 --> 00:16:09,640
Oh. Well, can you tell me
why you chose Yu Qing High School?

276
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:11,880
Why did you let Lu Xia go there?

277
00:16:11,960 --> 00:16:14,200
Do you think a normal senior high school
can help Lu Xia

278
00:16:14,280 --> 00:16:16,360
become a world-class tennis player?

279
00:16:16,880 --> 00:16:18,920
[scoffs]
"A world-class tennis player"?

280
00:16:19,920 --> 00:16:22,120
In fact, as long as he can play
in the senior high league,

281
00:16:22,200 --> 00:16:23,320
he will learn things.

282
00:16:24,040 --> 00:16:25,320
Is that really what you think?

283
00:16:25,400 --> 00:16:26,360
Of course.

284
00:16:26,760 --> 00:16:28,920
Don't underestimate
the senior high school tennis league.

285
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:30,160
[chuckles softly]

286
00:16:30,520 --> 00:16:33,000
I didn't expect you to think so highly
of the senior high league.

287
00:16:33,280 --> 00:16:35,360
It seems the chief editor
has better foresight than me.

288
00:16:35,440 --> 00:16:38,080
Please don't. I can't communicate
with the sophisticated people.

289
00:16:39,280 --> 00:16:42,280
Do you have plans for Lu Xia's future?

290
00:16:42,360 --> 00:16:43,760
-Me?
-Mm-hm.

291
00:16:43,840 --> 00:16:46,600
Do I look like a person
who always has plans?

292
00:16:47,680 --> 00:16:49,880
I only hope he doesn't follow my style
in tennis.

293
00:16:50,520 --> 00:16:53,640
Follow your style?
You mean he is imitating you?

294
00:16:57,680 --> 00:16:59,800
You know, you are really crafty.

295
00:17:00,480 --> 00:17:03,240
Remember, you lost the match.
I have told you enough.

296
00:17:04,920 --> 00:17:06,720
I'll come back, then.

297
00:17:06,800 --> 00:17:07,760
No problem.

298
00:17:07,839 --> 00:17:10,200
But you have to give me something
related to Hua Chenyu

299
00:17:10,280 --> 00:17:12,240
if you want to come back in.

300
00:17:12,760 --> 00:17:15,079
No problem, I will get you what you want.

301
00:17:15,160 --> 00:17:16,040
[Xiangqian] Let's go.

302
00:17:16,720 --> 00:17:18,359
[Sha] Can you please give me
a plastic bag?

303
00:17:18,440 --> 00:17:20,240
[Xiangqian] No need.
You can take it as it is.

304
00:17:20,319 --> 00:17:21,720
Just remember to give it back to me.

305
00:17:22,720 --> 00:17:25,000
[blenders whirring]

306
00:17:31,119 --> 00:17:32,839
[whirring continues]

307
00:17:38,800 --> 00:17:40,800
[upbeat music]

308
00:17:47,960 --> 00:17:49,960
[Yan Zhiming] Hmm. I finally succeeded.

309
00:17:59,200 --> 00:18:00,720
[Coach Qi] Thank you for your hard work

310
00:18:00,800 --> 00:18:01,840
while I was away.

311
00:18:02,120 --> 00:18:05,120
Ma'am, I am a lot more relieved
since you came back.

312
00:18:05,400 --> 00:18:07,240
[exhales sharply]
I have observed the players.

313
00:18:07,720 --> 00:18:09,240
Everyone is in good condition.

314
00:18:09,320 --> 00:18:10,600
We also have some new members.

315
00:18:11,400 --> 00:18:12,240
That's right.

316
00:18:12,320 --> 00:18:15,560
We recruited many new players
for this year's national league.

317
00:18:16,160 --> 00:18:19,440
Baiyang and Qiao Chen
are making rapid progress.

318
00:18:20,040 --> 00:18:21,400
After seeing the matches...

319
00:18:21,840 --> 00:18:24,480
I think they are ready
to be main players in our team.

320
00:18:25,560 --> 00:18:28,840
Apart from training,
the players should also get good grades.

321
00:18:29,280 --> 00:18:30,400
This is very important.

322
00:18:30,480 --> 00:18:33,360
Only those who pass the qualifiers
and have good grades...

323
00:18:34,120 --> 00:18:35,600
can take part in the national league.

324
00:18:35,960 --> 00:18:37,560
Siyang, please remember that.

325
00:18:39,280 --> 00:18:40,240
I will try my best.

326
00:18:40,800 --> 00:18:41,840
[inhales sharply]

327
00:18:41,920 --> 00:18:42,880
As the team captain,

328
00:18:43,760 --> 00:18:45,760
you should not only
focus on your own training,

329
00:18:46,880 --> 00:18:48,640
but also know
when to ask your team for help.

330
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:50,920
Don't leave everything to yourself.

331
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:52,280
Oh, speaking of...

332
00:18:52,360 --> 00:18:55,520
Yan has a unique understanding
of training.

333
00:18:56,080 --> 00:18:59,240
So I would like him to participate
in making future plans for training.

334
00:18:59,320 --> 00:19:00,320
What do you think, ma'am?

335
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:01,520
Mm-hm.
[inhales sharply]

336
00:19:01,600 --> 00:19:05,000
I have seen Yan Zhiming's plan.
It is very good for the team.

337
00:19:05,440 --> 00:19:08,200
So I would like you and Yan
to arrange the upcoming training.

338
00:19:08,680 --> 00:19:10,040
I will be supporting you.

339
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:12,440
Thank you, ma'am.

340
00:19:14,160 --> 00:19:16,160
[light music]

341
00:19:19,160 --> 00:19:21,000
[Yan Zhiming] I have made
a new training plan.

342
00:19:21,920 --> 00:19:24,120
Jiale, please help me demonstrate it.

343
00:19:24,600 --> 00:19:26,200
-Hmm?
-Mm-hm.

344
00:19:29,520 --> 00:19:31,160
No wonder you keep staring at me.

345
00:19:31,520 --> 00:19:33,320
You want to use me as an example.

346
00:19:34,760 --> 00:19:36,840
Everyone's techniques are different
from one another.

347
00:19:37,720 --> 00:19:39,800
Jiale is a flexible player.

348
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:42,960
Dayong is good at defending and attacking.

349
00:19:43,440 --> 00:19:45,320
Zhuo Zhi is a skillful player.

350
00:19:45,800 --> 00:19:48,360
But no matter how confident you may be
about your skills,

351
00:19:48,760 --> 00:19:51,120
the most important thing in a match
is the execution.

352
00:19:51,680 --> 00:19:55,600
The execution depends
on physical strength and reaction time.

353
00:19:56,240 --> 00:19:57,080
Mmm.

354
00:19:58,200 --> 00:20:00,600
If you put these sandbags on each leg,

355
00:20:01,360 --> 00:20:02,880
they will add one kilo to your weight.

356
00:20:06,600 --> 00:20:09,600
[scoffs]
How can such a thing cause me any trouble?

357
00:20:09,680 --> 00:20:11,200
You are underestimating me.

358
00:20:12,760 --> 00:20:14,680
Don't brag about yourself
before trying it.

359
00:20:15,920 --> 00:20:18,120
[Yan Zhiming] I prepared tennis balls
of different colors,

360
00:20:18,600 --> 00:20:21,160
as well as cones
with corresponding colors.

361
00:20:21,520 --> 00:20:22,960
When the machine shoots out the ball,

362
00:20:23,400 --> 00:20:25,440
you should aim for the corresponding cone.

363
00:20:25,520 --> 00:20:27,000
If you fail to do so, you lose.

364
00:20:27,120 --> 00:20:29,840
Let's have Jiale show it to us.

365
00:20:30,320 --> 00:20:32,160
Okay. Watch me.

366
00:20:32,720 --> 00:20:34,720
[upbeat music]

367
00:20:38,800 --> 00:20:39,880
Red.

368
00:20:46,560 --> 00:20:47,640
[Tang Jiale] Hmm.

369
00:20:49,160 --> 00:20:50,360
[whooshes]

370
00:20:51,040 --> 00:20:52,000
Blue.

371
00:20:53,600 --> 00:20:55,200
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

372
00:20:57,280 --> 00:20:58,200
Mmm.

373
00:20:59,120 --> 00:21:00,920
How is that? Is he good?

374
00:21:01,840 --> 00:21:03,280
He has good dynamic visual acuity.

375
00:21:03,760 --> 00:21:05,080
You seem to know a lot.

376
00:21:05,640 --> 00:21:07,560
But as for hitting speed
and reaction time,

377
00:21:07,640 --> 00:21:09,280
nobody can do it better than Jiale.

378
00:21:09,560 --> 00:21:13,160
Do you feel lucky to have
such a player with you on the team?

379
00:21:13,640 --> 00:21:15,480
The effect of the added weight
is about to show.

380
00:21:16,480 --> 00:21:17,480
[grunts]

381
00:21:17,760 --> 00:21:21,040
It is starting to be a little difficult.

382
00:21:21,680 --> 00:21:24,640
You are feeling the one kilo
on your feet, right?

383
00:21:24,720 --> 00:21:25,560
Mm-hm.

384
00:21:26,200 --> 00:21:27,680
Can I take it off?

385
00:21:27,760 --> 00:21:28,840
Of course not.

386
00:21:29,240 --> 00:21:30,800
Hmm. Okay.

387
00:21:31,720 --> 00:21:32,680
Come on.

388
00:21:33,280 --> 00:21:34,400
[whooshes]

389
00:21:34,760 --> 00:21:35,680
Red.

390
00:21:36,280 --> 00:21:37,920
-Shouldn't it be blue?
-Huh?

391
00:21:38,400 --> 00:21:39,240
[gasps]

392
00:21:43,040 --> 00:21:43,880
Huh?

393
00:21:47,480 --> 00:21:51,160
Yan, that's impossible.
This is obviously red.

394
00:21:51,560 --> 00:21:55,080
No matter what the color of the ball is,
you still didn't hit it, right?

395
00:21:55,640 --> 00:21:58,720
But you were distracting me
from the outside.

396
00:21:59,280 --> 00:22:02,120
If someone shouts "hook" in the game,

397
00:22:02,440 --> 00:22:04,920
-will you do as he says?
-All right.

398
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:08,160
Along with physical fatigue,
your judgment will be poorer as well.

399
00:22:08,640 --> 00:22:11,440
[Yan Zhiming]
No one can prevent this from happening.

400
00:22:11,720 --> 00:22:14,320
The only way to deal with it
is to improve your physical strength,

401
00:22:14,720 --> 00:22:17,960
so that you can have
precise judgment all the time.

402
00:22:19,040 --> 00:22:19,960
[sighs]

403
00:22:20,320 --> 00:22:21,200
I was wrong.

404
00:22:21,720 --> 00:22:23,760
You can't just depend on training
to be stronger.

405
00:22:24,160 --> 00:22:25,040
You should also...

406
00:22:26,480 --> 00:22:27,600
take care of your nutrition.

407
00:22:30,240 --> 00:22:31,240
[sniffs]

408
00:22:32,160 --> 00:22:33,240
So, what is it?

409
00:22:33,800 --> 00:22:35,760
Drink it and you will know.

410
00:22:36,720 --> 00:22:37,600
Oh.

411
00:22:40,240 --> 00:22:41,280
[gulps]

412
00:22:46,320 --> 00:22:47,400
Mm-hm.

413
00:22:47,720 --> 00:22:48,680
Here you are.

414
00:22:54,400 --> 00:22:56,400
[suspenseful music]

415
00:23:02,560 --> 00:23:03,680
[Tang Jiale screams]

416
00:23:03,880 --> 00:23:07,080
It is so bitter!

417
00:23:08,760 --> 00:23:10,400
I forgot to introduce it to you.

418
00:23:10,800 --> 00:23:13,160
[Yan Zhiming] This is my surprise for you,

419
00:23:13,240 --> 00:23:14,560
my specially made vegetable juice.

420
00:23:15,120 --> 00:23:16,880
We can call it "Yan-juice" for now.

421
00:23:17,640 --> 00:23:19,400
It has bitter gourd paste...

422
00:23:20,280 --> 00:23:22,680
and over 40 kinds of ingredients.

423
00:23:22,760 --> 00:23:24,320
They are all good for our body.

424
00:23:29,880 --> 00:23:30,760
[relieved sigh]

425
00:23:30,960 --> 00:23:31,960
The juice is pretty good.

426
00:23:32,600 --> 00:23:34,720
You may feel dizzy after drinking this,

427
00:23:35,040 --> 00:23:36,800
but you will gain lots of strength.

428
00:23:37,560 --> 00:23:39,400
Consider your current condition.

429
00:23:40,600 --> 00:23:42,520
Yan-juice seems to have a better effect

430
00:23:42,920 --> 00:23:44,000
on your spiritual status.

431
00:23:44,720 --> 00:23:47,840
In a match,
one's spirit is very important.

432
00:23:48,320 --> 00:23:49,920
It is beyond my expectations...

433
00:23:50,320 --> 00:23:51,840
for Yan-juice to have such an effect.

434
00:23:52,200 --> 00:23:53,600
-Xinglong.
-[gasps]

435
00:23:54,120 --> 00:23:56,360
You are next. Don't be afraid.

436
00:24:01,080 --> 00:24:02,200
Burning!

437
00:24:06,280 --> 00:24:07,960
[thwacking]

438
00:24:09,720 --> 00:24:11,360
[grunting]

439
00:24:15,640 --> 00:24:16,720
[screams]

440
00:24:17,600 --> 00:24:18,480
[gasps]

441
00:24:20,760 --> 00:24:22,280
[gulps]

442
00:24:23,400 --> 00:24:24,360
[relieved sigh]

443
00:24:25,240 --> 00:24:27,560
It is so bitter!

444
00:24:28,120 --> 00:24:30,040
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

445
00:24:37,680 --> 00:24:38,960
[gulps]

446
00:24:40,920 --> 00:24:41,960
[Baiyang groans]

447
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:44,200
It is so bitter!

448
00:24:47,680 --> 00:24:48,720
[sighs]

449
00:24:48,800 --> 00:24:50,080
[Dayong] It is so bitter!

450
00:24:51,880 --> 00:24:54,240
[Qiao Chen sobs]
It is so bitter!

451
00:24:57,120 --> 00:24:58,320
The ball went too fast.

452
00:25:00,440 --> 00:25:01,600
I have been expecting it.

453
00:25:02,120 --> 00:25:03,840
Mmm. Come on.

454
00:25:04,920 --> 00:25:06,080
[exhales sharply]

455
00:25:08,080 --> 00:25:10,080
[suspenseful music]

456
00:25:11,840 --> 00:25:13,240
-[gulps]
-[chimes]

457
00:25:13,880 --> 00:25:14,960
It is tasty.

458
00:25:15,440 --> 00:25:16,520
[gasps]

459
00:25:16,880 --> 00:25:18,680
No wonder you are a genius.

460
00:25:21,080 --> 00:25:22,360
You are really my close friend.

461
00:25:25,080 --> 00:25:26,440
[gulping]

462
00:25:26,760 --> 00:25:29,400
Hi, Chief Editor.
I am now near their training court.

463
00:25:29,480 --> 00:25:32,520
I will show you their real strength
in everyday training.

464
00:25:35,480 --> 00:25:37,400
-[Qiao Chen] Too bitter.
-[Baiyang] Really bitter.

465
00:25:37,880 --> 00:25:39,720
-[Tang Jiale] How bitter!
-[Dayong] Too bitter!

466
00:25:39,800 --> 00:25:41,680
[Chief Editor]
This is their real strength?

467
00:25:41,760 --> 00:25:43,280
No, Chief Editor.

468
00:25:43,480 --> 00:25:45,640
-Usually, they are not like this.
-[Xinglong] How bitter!

469
00:25:45,720 --> 00:25:47,160
I... Uh...

470
00:25:47,560 --> 00:25:49,440
[Sha] Hmm. Ah!

471
00:25:49,520 --> 00:25:53,080
I will show you, Chief Editor,
the real genius that Yu Qing is.

472
00:25:53,160 --> 00:25:54,320
Over there.

473
00:25:57,440 --> 00:25:59,760
Look, he is Lu Xia.

474
00:25:59,840 --> 00:26:01,000
He is a real genius.

475
00:26:01,080 --> 00:26:02,840
He can represent the real strength
of Yu Qing.

476
00:26:03,360 --> 00:26:04,840
[grunts]

477
00:26:06,440 --> 00:26:07,440
[gasps]

478
00:26:09,440 --> 00:26:10,440
[sighs]

479
00:26:16,640 --> 00:26:17,480
Hmm.

480
00:26:21,760 --> 00:26:22,680
[gasps]

481
00:26:25,240 --> 00:26:26,720
[gulps]

482
00:26:29,520 --> 00:26:30,920
-[Lu Xia groans]
-[gasps]

483
00:26:31,520 --> 00:26:33,240
[Chief Editor]
Is that your so-called genius?

484
00:26:33,640 --> 00:26:35,000
I think you are a fool.

485
00:26:35,360 --> 00:26:37,200
-Come back immediately.
-No, Chief Editor...

486
00:26:37,720 --> 00:26:38,720
Let me explain it to you.

487
00:26:38,800 --> 00:26:40,160
-Chief Editor.
-[Lu Xia] How bitter.

488
00:26:40,240 --> 00:26:42,680
-[Sha] Chief Editor, it is not like this.
-[Lu Xian] How bitter.

489
00:26:42,760 --> 00:26:44,400
-Chief Editor, please listen to me.
-Yan.

490
00:26:45,040 --> 00:26:46,040
What are you doing?

491
00:26:47,120 --> 00:26:48,120
Captain.

492
00:26:48,840 --> 00:26:53,240
This is the nutritional juice
I invented for everyone.

493
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:56,120
-You should taste it.
-Okay.

494
00:26:59,440 --> 00:27:00,960
[Siyang gulps]

495
00:27:02,840 --> 00:27:04,440
[gasps, sighs]

496
00:27:07,840 --> 00:27:09,040
[inhales sharply]

497
00:27:11,960 --> 00:27:12,880
[Siyang sighs]

498
00:27:12,960 --> 00:27:13,880
Do you like it?

499
00:27:15,760 --> 00:27:16,760
It is good.

500
00:27:17,640 --> 00:27:19,240
-Yan.
-Hm?

501
00:27:19,320 --> 00:27:20,880
[Siyang] I believe in your abilities

502
00:27:20,960 --> 00:27:22,120
and I support you as well.

503
00:27:22,840 --> 00:27:24,120
As for the juice...

504
00:27:25,200 --> 00:27:28,520
it can be the team's regular
nutritional supplement.

505
00:27:29,000 --> 00:27:31,080
But remember, only from time to time.

506
00:27:31,680 --> 00:27:32,760
Okay, Captain.

507
00:27:33,280 --> 00:27:35,400
Then, twice a week?

508
00:27:35,480 --> 00:27:36,400
[gasps]

509
00:27:36,480 --> 00:27:38,880
Once a week. We can discuss it.

510
00:27:39,320 --> 00:27:40,200
[soft chuckle]

511
00:27:40,640 --> 00:27:43,560
Taking a nutritional supplement
once a week is not enough.

512
00:27:44,160 --> 00:27:46,440
Once a week.
There is no need to discuss it.

513
00:27:48,880 --> 00:27:49,760
Okay, Captain.

514
00:27:49,880 --> 00:27:51,640
Then, I will invent a concentrated one.

515
00:27:52,160 --> 00:27:54,240
[Siyang groans, clears throat]

516
00:27:56,680 --> 00:27:58,720
It seems the captain
likes this juice as well.

517
00:28:00,040 --> 00:28:00,920
That's right.

518
00:28:01,560 --> 00:28:02,720
-Hmm.
-[snickers]

519
00:28:06,680 --> 00:28:09,360
[Yan Zhiming] Everyone seems
a lot more energetic

520
00:28:09,440 --> 00:28:10,920
after drinking the juice.

521
00:28:11,000 --> 00:28:14,240
Then I will continue
to talk about physical training.

522
00:28:14,920 --> 00:28:15,760
Xinglong.

523
00:28:16,320 --> 00:28:18,840
You always hold the racket loosely
when hitting balls.

524
00:28:19,280 --> 00:28:21,520
You need to strengthen
your forearm muscles.

525
00:28:22,400 --> 00:28:23,520
Baiyang, Dayong.

526
00:28:24,080 --> 00:28:26,280
You should pay attention to forward
and backward movement.

527
00:28:26,640 --> 00:28:29,360
Jiale and Zhuo Zhi should pay attention
to the left and right movement.

528
00:28:29,720 --> 00:28:33,120
Qiao Chen, if you only use 70 percent
of your strength when hitting balls,

529
00:28:33,480 --> 00:28:34,960
you will be more accurate.

530
00:28:36,960 --> 00:28:39,360
