674
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:33,320
so the Golden Partners
will stay together this year.

675
00:36:33,920 --> 00:36:34,880
[sighs]

676
00:36:34,960 --> 00:36:37,440
I kind of expect to compete
with Xing Yao High School.

677
00:36:38,280 --> 00:36:40,640
If we can play together,
we will be sure to win this time.

678
00:36:40,720 --> 00:36:41,600
[exhales sharply]

679
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:45,320
Mm-hm. In fact, playing doubles is great.

680
00:36:45,400 --> 00:36:47,040
There will be someone helping you

681
00:36:47,120 --> 00:36:49,360
